### 1. Create mock model config
POST http://localhost:8000/api/model-configs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workspace_id": "demo-workspace",
  "organization_id": null,
  "name": "默认 Mock 模型",
  "provider": "mock",
  "api_base_url": null,
  "api_key": null,
  "model_name": "mock-model",
  "use_case": "default",
  "temperature": 0.7,
  "max_tokens": 1200,
  "is_default": true
}

### 2. Test model config
POST http://localhost:8000/api/model-configs/{{config_id}}/test

### 3. List model configs
GET http://localhost:8000/api/model-configs?workspace_id=demo-workspace

### 4. Create OpenAI-compatible model config example
POST http://localhost:8000/api/model-configs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workspace_id": "demo-workspace",
  "organization_id": null,
  "name": "自定义 OpenAI 兼容模型",
  "provider": "openai_compatible",
  "api_base_url": "https://api.openai.com/v1",
  "api_key": "replace-with-your-api-key",
  "model_name": "gpt-4.1-mini",
  "use_case": "content_producer",
  "temperature": 0.7,
  "max_tokens": 1200,
  "is_default": false
}

